data.description: This corner detached home is nestled in a gated community of Bella Bonita at Sweetwater and Plaza Bonita, with a great school district, within minutes of the shopping mall, freeway exits, and grocery stores. This home features tile floors throughout the first level. The kitchen offers top gas stove, stainless steel vent hood, stainless steel appliances, huge island that opens to the family room.  All bedrooms are upstairs. Washer and dryer located in the garage. Great size backyard with pergola and room for gardening.
